Supreme Lord. It is for others who are not at this state; for them the gradual process of renunciation, knowledge, meditation and realization of the Supersoul and Brahman should be followed. But as far as Bhagavad-g\xe2\x80\x9dt\xe2\x88\x92 is concerned, it is the direct method that is stressed. Everyone is \nadvised to take to the direct method and surrender unto the Supreme Personality of Godhead, K\xe2\x80\x9e\xc5\x92\xe2\x80\x9aa.'

